    {
      "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-8016-87c8-e500616494bb",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "E-learning has made it possible to democratize education across multiple learners with different knowledge, goals and abilities. However, adopting one-size fits all solutions to learners in this context is also challenging, which is an argument for Recommender Systems. The goal of the work is to propose a transductive support vector regression hybrid recommender system.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-8016-87c8-e500616494bb",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "d4fc3dcb-cf31-4fbb-a7fa-2153edb543e5"
        },
        "created_time": "2025-03-09T22:09:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2025-03-09T22:13:00.000Z",
