    {
      "id": "1b14750c-f3ba-8031-abf9-dbec79a214e8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper introduces a set of optimization techniques at multiple stages of the RS: one-source denoising, modified anarchy society optimization, sequential pattern strategy. All in all, the data leads habits and interest, later used to make recomnnedations to learners. Authors eprform extensive validation on public datasets (including OULAD). Overall, system achieves 82 to 98% accuracy and 5% to 19.2% MAE.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
